<para style="q1">

<verse number="11" style="v" />Yahweh swore a sure oath to David,</para>

<para style="q1">a sure oath that he will not revoke:</para>

<para style="q1">"I will place one of your descendants on your throne.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="12" style="v" />If your sons keep my covenant</para>

<para style="q1">and the laws that I will teach them,</para>

<para style="q1">their children also will sit on your throne forevermore."</para>
